{"tid":563791,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"最能代表香港既導演真係得王家衛一個","createTime":"2018-02-17T09:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T11:27:58.000Z","uid":59014,"like":113,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"8d5ba9103de7f342a94af783f10ea6738fec1774","tid":563791,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T09:30:29.000Z","msg":"同意 = 正評<br />\n<br />\n個種唯美，同舊代下既香港，同情感<br />\n<br />\n真係比王家衛拿揑得好好，稱佢做藝術家都合理<br />\n<br />\n對白設計百聽不厭，每次睇完重慶森林、阿飛正傳、春光乍洩個心都好沉，感受好大"},{"pid":"6aff81ede2f34963b99f30956d6b48a9cde0ef1d","tid":563791,"uid":6988,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T09:31:59.000Z","msg":"早期星爺我覺得都係"},{"pid":"7d68996ebe8db7499b828809c43795052ae6d8c9","tid":563791,"uid":80566,"like":51,"dislike":3,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T09:33:05.000Z","msg":"杜琪峰？"},{"pid":"253f8325297b4a6909e5af11df516acc1190a572","tid":563791,"uid":27915,"like":53,"dislike":3,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T09:36:54.000Z","msg":"代表？<br />\n佢係叻 但樓上話杜琪峰先代表到香港喎<br />\n啲黑社會/警匪片 一諗港產片係諗起呢啲先"},{"pid":"c77e86babe12ec5bd0d1ec54fd92d34519f84771","tid":563791,"uid":5077,"like":5,"dislike":26,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T09:48:30.000Z","msg":"問過葉念琛未呀"},{"pid":"c976b6d1aeaa23fce8c611600d6b304762a7695f","tid":563791,"uid":134683,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"邊個令到鬼佬覺得香港電影=雙槍？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/17/175329_81e8704e8fa28517f77d234a2daafc8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F17%2F175329_81e8704e8fa28517f77d234a2daafc8a.png&h=404beb66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef221a01c7fe47991ef0c828e3eff054eeafb6cc","tid":563791,"uid":34377,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T10:10:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>杜琪峰？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吳宇森<br />\n<br />\n徐克"},{"pid":"1890e771bb54b1713b6f67f78