8d38897c99bb695d4ba8ea4fdfe51","tid":563791,"uid":34511,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T12:36:41.000Z","msg":"大部分香港人都唔識欣賞王家衛，比返王精衛佢哋算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701bb92e2603538ef1a3dab774e8d37246e3f448","tid":563791,"uid":40804,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T12:43:04.000Z","msg":"重慶森林小試牛刀<br />\n春光乍洩刻骨銘心<br />\n花樣年華登峰造極<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af46ba6d0c8ed04d7d49b030276bcd977a1e474a","tid":563791,"uid":65343,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:02:31.000Z","msg":"佢係香港玩藝術，玩調度等最有特色，作品既美學媲美班外國名導演果個。<br />\n<br />\n但你話代表香港，我會投杜sir, 韋家輝呢pair一票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad4996ecc9d219c4907e360a6acfc54f92315fa","tid":563791,"uid":8009,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:04:10.000Z","msg":"只可以話佢係藝術家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a27afe5a03c949b6674ea41fdf3b1e6cabfc3f","tid":563791,"uid":55594,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:04:51.000Z","msg":"香港驕傲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87bb091e04ab3244c3f6cb2e3a985cf54e75dc4","tid":563791,"uid":134683,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"cbdfac1c7986cc0cd59cbdfc08662f8a46e0f799","tid":563791,"uid":159266,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c976b6d1aeaa23fce8c611600d6b304762a7695f","tid":563791,"uid":134683,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"邊個令到鬼佬覺得香港電影=雙槍？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/17/175329_81e8704e8fa28517f77d234a2daafc8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F17%2F175329_81e8704e8fa28517f77d234a2daafc8a.png&h=404beb66&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T11:28:38.000Z","msg":"港產片根本唔應該被定型做雙鎗動作片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢個套追捕爛撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:39:15.000Z","msg":"點都唔夠太平輪爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢巔峰時期果幾套的確係經典<br />\n威尼斯影展個終身成就獎唔係亂頒<br />\n但吳宇森既成就就只係得咁多<br />\n佢跟本一早已經追唔上時代<br />\nMI2仲用實物模型拍架飛機都夠膽死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本身好迷80年代吳宇森<br />\n辣手神探梁朝偉同發哥喺倉庫槍戰果幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過今日既佢..."},{"pid":"a4558335160a5683fdd57a937a7586d0b69f1ef2","tid":563791,"uid":31001,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"正撚到仆街<br />\n但唔係個個識欣賞"},{"pid":"dd5674f838c8f95e54be7c5e3bca579e54714bae","tid":563791,"uid":68738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c77e86babe12ec5bd0d1ec54fd92d34519f84771","tid":563791,"uid":5077,"like":5,"dislike":26,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T09:48:30.000Z","msg":"問過葉念琛未呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37088f59384e42ae0318db08f208686c0d92cb6d","tid":563791,"uid":105366,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"c77e86babe12ec5bd0d1ec54fd92d34519f84771","tid":563791,"uid":5077,"like":5,"dislike":26,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T09:48:30.000Z","msg":"問過葉念琛未呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:44:31.000Z","msg":"維港以外冇人識你喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大學時代，啲鬼仔電影迷同學，一聽到有戲係John Woo(吳宇森)、Tsui Hak(徐克)、Ringo Lam(林嶺東)即刻要我借餅VHS帶佢地睇。"},{"pid":"29b998ce94ab5d2eb7ee75ef6d3f05cccba24e90","tid":563791,"uid":51121,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"許鞍華先有得鬥<br />\n話杜琪峰都on9 香港真係得黑社會咩<br />\n<br />\n不過王家衛啲野比較普世價值 好少特別探討香港既問題 就算講回歸都係用比較普遍人性角度去講。"},{"pid":"3122fe7ac66bf177f8ff68631a89a7488be15043","tid":563791,"uid":61660,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:07:05.000Z","msg":"最代表係王晶就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡直係香港電影點運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5a9ced8f4229b0c1ab962c1c6c233c39b62f43","tid":563791,"uid":61660,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最代表係王晶就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡直係香港電影點運作既縮影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"85c4c33ae53d17d4da2a6ed0df653321cb12c398","tid":563791,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"29b998ce94ab5d2eb7ee75ef6d3f05cccba24e90","tid":563791,"uid":51121,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"許鞍華先有得鬥<br />\n話杜琪峰都on9 香港真係得黑社會咩<br />\n<br />\n不過王家衛啲野比較普世價值 好少特別探討香港既問題 就算講回歸都係用比較普遍人性角度去講。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:08:58.000Z","msg":"唔揀杜sir主因都係呢個，杜sir的確幫左香港好多去發揚黑幫/警匪題材，但始終呢類題材唔係大眾類，體驗唔到香港人民社會 同文化特色，去宣傳香港電影亦都唔係咁適合。"},{"pid":"b17501bb34766f08c5140f9c6863ae4f08e1b638","tid":563791,"uid":59014,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"85c4c33ae53d17d4da2a6ed0df653321cb12c398","tid":563791,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"29b998ce94ab5d2eb7ee75ef6d3f05cccba24e90","tid":563791,"uid":51121,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"許鞍華先有得鬥<br />\n話杜琪峰都on9 香港真係得黑社會咩<br />\n<br />\n不過王家衛啲野比較普世價值 好少特別探討香港既問題 就算講回歸都係用比較普遍人性角度去講。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:08:58.000Z","msg":"唔揀杜sir主因都係呢個，杜sir的確幫左香港好多去發揚黑幫/警匪題材，但始終呢類題材唔係大眾類，體驗唔到香港人民社會 同文化特色，去宣傳香港電影亦都唔係咁適合。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:16:09.000Z","msg":"相反睇王家衛電影，將香港文化、中西交匯、多元化拍得好好，帶得出香港係個繁榮既星斗城市，每日都有唔同種族既人來人往，既疏離又熟悉既感覺。"},{"pid":"3a5f5f7a3d40bf6ba24445a46887e75a1e09263b","tid":563791,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef221a01c7fe47991ef0c828e3eff054eeafb6cc","tid":563791,"uid":34377,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T10:10:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>杜琪峰？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吳宇森<br />\n<br />\n徐克"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:18:23.000Z","msg":"呢兩個都算係叫代表左兩種好唔同既美學"},{"pid":"4dc6cc915f4fcb38ca1861ed0b38f34b9bafa8c5","tid":563791,"uid":48479,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"老實講，真係切切實實呈現到香港風味嘅王家衛電影只有早期嘅阿飛正傳、重慶森林同墮落天使，而只有後兩者係當代香港。<br />\n春光乍洩係帶香港情懷嘅拉美風情; 花樣年華同2046係經營出嚟嘅舊香港味，所呈現出嘅係一種orientalism多過係香港味。<br />\n當然我唔係話王家衛代表唔到香港，無可否認佢係香港喺國際影壇最成功嘅導演，但講到只有佢最代表到香港未免太目中無人。"},{"pid":"50a1c19cfb249d74f8a0be761d07ea817fb327ca","tid":563791,"uid":48479,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b17501bb34766f08c5140f9c6863ae4f08e1b638","tid":563791,"uid":59014,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"85c4c33ae53d17d4da2a6ed0df653321cb12c398","tid":563791,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"29b998ce94ab5d2eb7ee75ef6d3f05cccba24e90","tid":563791,"uid":51121,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"許鞍華先有得鬥<br />\n話杜琪峰都on9 香港真係得黑社會咩<br />\n<br />\n不過王家衛啲野比較普世價值 好少特別探討香港既問題 就算講回歸都係用比較普遍人性角度去講。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:08:58.000Z","msg":"唔揀杜sir主因都係呢個，杜sir的確幫左香港好多去發揚黑幫/警匪題材，但始終呢類題材唔係大眾類，體驗唔到香港人民社會 同文化特色，去宣傳香港電影亦都唔係咁適合。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:16:09.000Z","msg":"相反睇王家衛電影，將香港文化、中西交匯、多元化拍得好好，帶得出香港係個繁榮既星斗城市，每日都有唔同種族既人來人往，既疏離又熟悉既感覺。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:07:46.000Z","msg":"你似乎只係講緊重慶森林<br />\n我認同呢套係將香港拍得最有神采嘅電影，但拍埋姊妹作墮落天使之後，王家衛基本上放棄咗香港 (i mean當代)<br />\n反觀杜琪峯，你話佢反映唔到香港社會文化特色，實在太好笑。我建議你睇下無涯，聽下啲人(e.g. 賈樟柯)點講杜琪峯電影所呈現嘅香港"},{"pid":"3d95fb9cff7c0a1f6640e53af90c35191eea5f44","tid":563791,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:10:19.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0a89be878445059a8c11d86e57a176cec7a95456","tid":563791,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f5a9ced8f4229b0c1ab962c1c6c233c39b62f43","tid":563791,"uid":61660,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最代表係王晶就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡直係香港電影點運作既縮影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:10:24.000Z","msg":"佢套大戰拉斯為加斯同周星星個堆戲都好正"},{"pid":"3c9dbbae1bb0e65d53d2a4b8d12b2b5f0173400c","tid":563791,"uid":88999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:13:20.000Z","msg":"係以香港人角度揀定係亞洲／歐美角度揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔同角度可能出唔同嘅人選"},{"pid":"7a009260e6f056029f2b64b4d51812eda583b809","tid":563791,"uid":152367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:25:13.000Z","msg":"太耐先出到一套"},{"pid":"5d7f2dc27eae8ca3c7908285e3443fb673290b71","tid":563791,"uid":119405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:36:22.000Z","msg":"陳果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9a418e7ba5e09da8c682fc6c165d5105a7d3da","tid":563791,"uid":65343,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:40:10.000Z","msg":"樓上果啲係咪on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪無視杜sir同韋家輝間銀河映像既戲？<br />\n<br />\n其實話搵個最代表香港既導演都好on9架啦，但理性咁諗，王導既作品喺藝術層面上吸收唔少外國既技法，而主題上佢偏向係人既情感上。<br />\n<br />\n相反，杜sir 拍過既，先莫論好壞，題材廣，涉及香港元素既都一定多過王導先，例子有孤男寡女，文雀等，一定唔止樓上所講得警匪，黑幫囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (當然佔既係多)<br />\n<br />\n利申：兩個導演都好中意，同時佢地既電影都實"},{"pid":"70505cbdbd486c1ebd09ab5ee3314220e779b3a0","tid":563791,"uid":86587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"離地導演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5db357444773bcd7dd4c19cd9186e94534ed2f","tid":563791,"uid":65343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b9a418e7ba5e09da8c682fc6c165d5105a7d3da","tid":563791,"uid":65343,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:40:10.000Z","msg":"樓上果啲係咪on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪無視杜sir同韋家輝間銀河映像既戲？<br />\n<br />\n其實話搵個最代表香港既導演都好on9架啦，但理性咁諗，王導既作品喺藝術層面上吸收唔少外國既技法，而主題上佢偏向係人既情感上。<br />\n<br />\n相反，杜sir 拍過既，先莫論好壞，題材廣，涉及香港元素既都一定多過王導先，例子有孤男寡女，文雀等，一定唔止樓上所講得警匪，黑幫囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (當然佔既係多)<br />\n<br />\n利申：兩個導演都好中意，同時佢地既電影都實"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:43:25.000Z","msg":"未打晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都實在太唔同，無論技法定主題，但你夾硬話要拎個代表&quot;香港&quot;電影，我會揀杜sir囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e49d80bfb192ab1b20d7a4f9b9fb1d89b0272b","tid":563791,"uid":132587,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T17:00:03.000Z","msg":"代表香港電影既導演係杜琪峯<br />\n代表香港既電影導演係王家衛"},{"pid":"bcca7a83dc2f67158419ed7172b8329107c07913","tid":563791,"uid":65343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dc6cc915f4fcb38ca1861ed0b38f34b9bafa8c5","tid":563791,"uid":48479,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"老實講，真係切切實實呈現到香港風味嘅王家衛電影只有早期嘅阿飛正傳、重慶森林同墮落天使，而只有後兩者係當代香港。<br />\n春光乍洩係帶香港情懷嘅拉美風情; 花樣年華同2046係經營出嚟嘅舊香港味，所呈現出嘅係一種orientalism多過係香港味。<br />\n當然我唔係話王家衛代表唔到香港，無可否認佢係香港喺國際影壇最成功嘅導演，但講到只有佢最代表到香港未免太目中無人。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T17:04:20.000Z","msg":"香港最有特色，但唔等於最具香港特色"},{"pid":"b65f71b6f4b8b31082962a59d05a1bbb8e6d26f2","tid":563791,"uid":84323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T17:11:56.000Z","msg":"點解係無間道張圖唔係講緊劉偉強既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c7ea9cce5cf879afc437c5410c619a589209aa","tid":563791,"uid":53774,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T17:25:06.000Z","msg":"傻啦,香港根本唔配有王家衛<br />\n唔少香港觀眾都幾bad taste"},{"pid":"6eb0a3f3a86a5f4b2b5ad4670917bae1b1d318d9","tid":563791,"uid":150781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d87bb091e04ab3244c3f6cb2e3a985cf54e75dc4","tid":563791,"uid":134683,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"cbdfac1c7986cc0cd59cbdfc08662f8a46e0f799","tid":563791,"uid":159266,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c976b6d1aeaa23fce8c611600d6b304762a7695f","tid":563791,"uid":134683,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"邊個令到鬼佬覺得香港電影=雙槍？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/17/175329_81e8704e8fa28517f77d234a2daafc8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F17%2F175329_81e8704e8fa28517f77d234a2daafc8a.png&h=404beb66&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T11:28:38.000Z","msg":"港產片根本唔應該被定型做雙鎗動作片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢個套追捕爛撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:39:15.000Z","msg":"點都唔夠太平輪爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢巔峰時期果幾套的確係經典<br />\n威尼斯影展個終身成就獎唔係亂頒<br />\n但吳宇森既成就就只係得咁多<br />\n佢跟本一早已經追唔上時代<br />\nMI2仲用實物模型拍架飛機都夠膽死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本身好迷80年代吳宇森<br />\n辣手神探梁朝偉同發哥喺倉庫槍戰果幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過今日既佢..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T18:23:44.000Z","msg":"faceoff都仲okay，去到MI2已經開始回塘，冇新idea冇新思維。"},{"pid":"f93cdced6473c6112588adc9c5b8f792a3450c11","tid":563791,"uid":150781,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"50a1c19cfb249d74f8a0be761d07ea817fb327ca","tid":563791,"uid":48479,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b17501bb34766f08c5140f9c6863ae4f08e1b638","tid":563791,"uid":59014,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"85c4c33ae53d17d4da2a6ed0df653321cb12c398","tid":563791,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:08:58.000Z","msg":"唔揀杜sir主因都係呢個，杜sir的確幫左香港好多去發揚黑幫/警匪題材，但始終呢類題材唔係大眾類，體驗唔到香港人民社會 同文化特色，去宣傳香港電影亦都唔係咁適合。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:16:09.000Z","msg":"相反睇王家衛電影，將香港文化、中西交匯、多元化拍得好好，帶得出香港係個繁榮既星斗城市，每日都有唔同種族既人來人往，既疏離又熟悉既感覺。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:07:46.000Z","msg":"你似乎只係講緊重慶森林<br />\n我認同呢套係將香港拍得最有神采嘅電影，但拍埋姊妹作墮落天使之後，王家衛基本上放棄咗香港 (i mean當代)<br />\n反觀杜琪峯，你話佢反映唔到香港社會文化特色，實在太好笑。我建議你睇下無涯，聽下啲人(e.g. 賈樟柯)點講杜琪峯電影所呈現嘅香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T18:26:50.000Z","msg":"佢套文雀，雖然小本經營，但係拍得好有香港情懷，好多舊景，舊建築物，好多舊室內設計。"},{"pid":"4b4a6e0dc060ec81e8c5992360af73bd91cb825f","tid":563791,"uid":21260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"95c7ea9cce5cf879afc437c5410c619a589209aa","tid":563791,"uid":53774,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T17:25:06.000Z","msg":"傻啦,香港根本唔配有王家衛<br />\n唔少香港觀眾都幾bad taste"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T18:31:36.000Z","msg":"都唔知有冇一半香港人識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614990dd17990127f0189fd56cf7d1017bf0a314","tid":563791,"uid":2707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"s